data.description: POOL... do I need to say more? This luxury home is nestled in the Tall Timbers subdivision with its own neighborhood entrance. It features 5 bedrooms (home is set-up utilizing 6 bdrms) and 4 full bathrooms with a pool. Over 3,680 SF of living space on a large lot. Oversized and open living space features fireplace and wet bar. Entertain in style. Easy to clean and maintain marble finish concrete flooring. No carpet. Dining space with modern crystal lighting fixture and lots of natural light. Kitchen features double oven, dishwasher and electric cook top. Retreat to the lavish and large primary suite overlooking the pool. Downstairs primary suite has adjoining spa-like bathroom. Ensuite features massive walk-in shower, rain shower head, soaking tub and double vanity. Adjoining sitting room off primary bedroom can be used as dressing room, study, reading room or whatever you can dream. Complete with built-in shelving floor to ceiling. Upstairs features 4 large secondary bedrooms and 2 sets of Jack & Jill bathrooms. Detached recreation room is an exceptional space with a full bathroom, bar and upstairs loft storage. Step outside to your private and fenced built-in pool for these hot Louisiana days. New roof. Solar panels. Plenty of off-street parking. Entertainment possibilities and room usage are endless. This exceptional residence is available for private showing appointments.
